snippet.title: BaronVonGames
snippet.description:
Hello I'm Baron.

I like video games.  So I play and make videos on a great variety of games.  Everything from PC to console to mobile, and AAA to indie games.  I like them all. 

I also run the YouTube channel BaronVonTactics where I focus primarily on mobile gaming.  Check it out

Thanks for subscribing, and thanks for watching!
-Baron
